	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Savannah Ga</placeName> <date>April 30&#47;66</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd  Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
				<p>Knowing you like to be informed of every<lb/> <add>Hebrew</add>&#44; I take the liberty to advise you that the<lb/> Polish Congregation is about to build<lb/> a Synagogue&#44; and great effort will be made<lb/> to have the building <sic>don</sic> by <date>New Year</date>.<lb/> I have read in the Occident a month or so<lb/> back&#44; that <persName>Rev Mr S Gerstman</persName> is officiating<lb/> in the above Synagogue&#44; allow me to correct<lb/> this error&#44; that <persName>Mr. S. Gerstman</persName> never was<lb/> nor will be a Revd Preacher never a teacher.<lb/> To keep him out of the confederate service<lb/> the Jews <sic>don</sic> him the favor to let him<lb/> read on <date>Saturdays</date>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">Yours Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">M G Joseph</persName></p>
				<p>P.S. I am no member</p>
		</body>
